headline: Paycom price target lowered to $185 from $191 at Citi
summary: Citi lowered the firm’s price target on Paycom (PAYC) to $185 from $191 and keeps a Neutral rating on the shares. The firm adjusted models in the application software group after catching up with managements. Companies are facing a stable but uncertain demand environment, with some relief from the reopening of the U.S. government, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
